witter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21</a><br />\n2. 如果你選擇將10個電話重新打一次出黎，記得加+852<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. 成本低<br />\n2. 可以迫大家儲下唔同角度文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n1. 本地線唔會要大家post番個舉報cap圖出黎，少左第二次marketing機會 (which is fine)<br />\n2. 外國人參與國際線程度成疑，但我覺得以campaign之名，行宣傳之實。就咁講#chinazi，#culturalrevolution，老實講有d悶。"},{"pid":"7bac70b42292a50519c887026c287395f0db1c22","tid":1559133,"uid":25573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:10:23.000Z","msg":"City bu 全力支持"},{"pid":"826ba60ea878b651a68ba84d4d718e9b06a44d64","tid":1559133,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:10:59.000Z","msg":"sorry 借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩未食飯既同我入哂黎!!! 唔準有人餓住個肚!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《急推》 前線唔好餓死呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b9d5a3a43b1cf4d974a0b4d03856f324c5f7d63c","tid":1559133,"uid":190696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:24:36.000Z","msg":"支持啊喂"},{"pid":"8e78014eb2215cfdcbf95965cc9458503e37ccaa","tid":1559133,"uid":238198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T00:55:26.000Z","msg":"推呀，全力支持"},{"pid":"9040ba2468e52e13142cb6e07939668bdd1000a3","tid":1559133,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:35:02.000Z","msg":"繼續呼叫九龍塘人"},{"pid":"4358f024c6995f0bdeb0f69d17227927238d6103","tid":1559133,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:01:46.000Z","msg":"Pushhh"},{"pid":"f3d7ef20ed22e49932709e3333c20442cba61caa","tid":1559133,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"